Every code cell in this document was evaluated against QuantumFramework 2.0.0 \
before being written down; the numbers quoted are the framework's own output. \
Evaluate them yourself, then change the parameters and watch the physics \
respond.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"786be41a-6030-4650-8a30-ce0ff2d0f05f"]
